# Overview
[ranger](https://ranger.fm) integration for xonsh shell

## Installation

To install use pip:

``` bash
xpip install xontrib-ranger
```

## Usage
It adds `r` alias function. So commands like `cd` will work from broot.
``` bash
$ xontrib load ranger
$ r 
```

